<application>
  <id type="desktop">smc.desktop</id>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <summary>2D platform game that uses OpenGL in a style similar to Super Mario</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
        Secret Maryo Chronicles is an Open Source two-dimensional platform game
        with a design similar to classic computer games. SMC has computer
        support to a great degree by using an accelerated Open Graphics Library
        for the best possible graphic design and stock performance.

        Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>In-game editor</li>
        <li>Many levels</li>
        <li>Multiple Maryo stages</li>
        <li>Multiple overlords</li>
        <li>Great sound and music</li>
        <li>Save and load</li>
        <li>Get extra lives</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
